;A Brand New Tiles Experience
Čisće nowe dožiwjenje z kachličkami


;With Enhanced Tiles and Directory Tiles, Firefox provides users easy access to interesting, relevant content, whether it’s the sites they visit most or new sites for them to discover.
Z polěpšenymi kachličkami a zapisowymi kachličkami zmóžnja Firefox lochki přistup na zajimawy, relewantny wobsah, njech su sydła, kotrež so najhušćišo wopytuja abo nowe sydła, kotrež maja so hišće wotkrywać.


;What are Tiles?
Što su kachlički?


;When you open a new tab in Firefox, you see several rectangles that link to different websites.
Hdyž nowy rajtark w Firefox wočinjeće, widźiće wjacore praworóžki, kotrež na druhe websydła wotkazuja.


;Some people call them squares, windows or bookmarks; we call them Tiles.
Někotři ludźo mjenuja je kwadraty, wokna abo zapołožki; my mjenujemy je kachlički.


;What are Enhanced Tiles?
Što su polěpšene kachlički?


;Existing Firefox users will be offered a set of Enhanced Tiles based on their browsing history.
Wužiwarjam Firefox so sadźba polěpšenych kachličkow na zakładźe jich přehladowanskeje historije poskića.


;The Enhanced versions replace the default screenshot with a better image and are displayed only for sites that the user has visited.
Polěpšene wersije narunuja standardne foto wobrazowki z lěpšim wobrazom a zwobraznjuja so jenož za sydła, kotrež wužiwar je wopytał.


;The improved image is supplied by the site or partner and can include a logo plus a rollover image.
Polěpšeny wobraz staja so přez sydło abo wot partnera k dispoziciji a móže logo a wobraz ze znošnym efektom wobsahować.


;If you frequent Amazon.com, for example, you might see the Amazon logo or icon, instead of a screenshot.
Jeli na přikład často Amazon.com wopytujeće, wy móhł Amazonowe logo abo Amazonowy symbol město fota wobrazowki widźeć.


;What are Directory Tiles?
Što su zapisowe kachlički?


;New Firefox users are initially given a set of Directory Tiles as suggestions for sites that may be of interest to them.
Nowym wužiwarjam so na spočatku sadźba zapisowych kachličkow jako namjety za sydła podawa, kotrež su zajimawe za nich.


;Instead of displaying a blank set of Tiles, Firefox shows content from Mozilla and some Mozilla partners.
Město zo so prózdna sadźba kachličkow zwobraznja, Firefox pokazuje wobsah wot Mozilla a někotrych partnerow Mozilla.


;All partner content is marked as “sponsored” and users have complete control to edit or remove any Tile.
Wšón partnerski wobsah markěruje so jako “sponsorowany” a wužiwarjo maja połnu kontrolu nad wobdźěłowanjom abo wotstronjenjom kachlički.


;Respects your privacy
Respektuje wašu priwatnosć


;As with all Mozilla products, Tiles provide users with extensive control over their personal data.
Kaž pola wšěch produktow Mozilla, dawaja kachlički wužiwarjam wobšěrnu kontrolu nad jich wosobinskimi datami.


;Data collection is limited to the aggregate number of impressions, clicks and Tile placement.
Datowa zběrka wobmjezuje so na cyłkownu ličbu zaćišćow, kliknjenjow a na placěrowanje kachličkow.


;Nothing is ever personally identifiable. In other words, we don’t know who clicks on what.
Ničo wosobinske identifikujomne njeje. Hinak prajene, njewěmy, štóž na čo kliknje.


;We just know the total number of views and clicks an individual Tile receives. This helps us deliver the most interesting and relevant content.
Wěmy jenož cyłkownu ličbu wopytow a kliknjenjow, kotrež jednotliwa kachlička dóstawa. To nam pomha, najzajimawši a relewantny wobsah k dispoziciji stajić.


;You can deactivate click and impression tracking by clicking on the gear icon on the top right corner of the new tab page, and selecting Classic to show only unenhanced History Tiles or Blank mode.
Móžeće slědowanje kliknjenjow a zaćišćow znjemóžnić, kliknjo na symbol ze zubatym koleskom w róžku horjeka naprawo strony noweho rajtarka a wuběrajo Klasisce, zo byšće jenož njepolěpšene kachlički historije abo prózdny modus pokazał.


;Frequently Asked Questions
Huste prašenja


;Are you tracking users now?
Slědujeće nětko wužiwarjow?


;We only collect data from the New Tab page in aggregate form, meaning no data is personally identifiable.
Zběramy daty ze strony noweho rajtarka jenož w zjatej formje, t. r. daty njeidentifikuja nikoho wosobinsce.


;What data is being collected?
Kotre daty so zběraja?


;Aggregate data from the New Tab page includes impressions, clicks and tile placement.
Zjate daty ze strony noweho rajtarka wobsahuja zaćišće, kliknjenja a placěrowanje kachličkow.


;What data is collected when I opt out?
Kotre daty so zběraja, jeli wužiwar njepřihłosuje?


;No data is collected when a user chooses to opt out of the enhanced Tiles experience.
Žane daty so njezběraja, jeli wužiwar rozsudźa, dožiwjenju polěpšenych kachličkow njepřihłosować.


;Where can I learn more?
Hdźe móžu wjace wo tym zhonić?


